item.title: Hello World
item.description: Hello from Hugo! A Section Here’s a simple titled section where you can place whatever information you want. You can use inline HTML if you want, but really there’s not much that Markdown can’t do. Showing off with Markdown A full cheat sheet can be found here or through Google. There are some easy examples for styling, though. I can’t emphasize that enough. Creating links or inline code blocks are very straightforward.
